---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About me as senior Laravel developer" description="Welcome to Lzo Media, where innovation meets expertise! I'm Stefan, a seasoned Laravel developer based in the United Kingdom with over 13 years of hands-on experience. Here's a glimpse into what I bring to the table:">

	<main class="stack gap-20 wrapper about">
		<Hero
			title="About"
			tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
		></Hero>

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					Hello there! I’m <strong>Stefan</strong>, a <strong>senior PHP and Python developer</strong> from Romania, now based in the <strong>United Kingdom</strong>. With over <strong>13 years of experience</strong> in software development, I specialize in building robust <strong>enterprise applications</strong> that solve real-world problems.
				</p>
				<p>
					I have a genuine passion for coding, particularly in <strong>PHP</strong> and <strong>Python</strong>, which are my go-to languages for creating scalable and efficient solutions. <strong>Nothing excites me more</strong> than tackling complex challenges head-on, using the best programming language for the job to ensure optimal performance and functionality.
				</p>
				<p>
					Despite my love for puzzles, I approach every project with utmost seriousness. Each opportunity to code is a chance to grow and refine my skills as a developer. Whether it’s crafting a new feature in <strong>PHP</strong> or developing a data processing application in <strong>Python</strong>, I am committed to delivering the highest quality solutions that meet and exceed client expectations.
				</p>
				<p>
					If you’re searching for a dedicated <strong>PHP and Python developer</strong> available for hire in London, look no further! I’m ready to dive into your coding challenges and help bring your vision to life. Let’s collaborate on your next project and achieve outstanding results together!
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title" title="My educations">Education</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					<strong>University of Bucharest</strong>
					<br />
					<span>Computer Science</span>
					<br />
					<span>2010 - 2014</span>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<ul>
					<li>PHP - spanning over 15 years of experience</li>
					<li>Python - 7 years of experience</li>
					<li>IoT - spanning over 3 years of experience</li>
					<li>NLP & AI - 4 years of experience</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="section-title">Certifications</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					<strong>CloudAmpq Certified Developer, 2023</strong><br />
					<strong>AWS Certified Solutions Architect, 2020</strong><br />
					<strong>Amazon Web Services, 2018</strong><br />
					<strong>Google Cloud Certified Associate Cloud Engineer, 2018</strong><br />
					<strong>Magento 2 Certification, 2018</strong><br />
					<strong>Laravel Certification, 2016</strong>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
		b, strong {
			color: var(--gray-400);
		}
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	.button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--primary-color);
		color: #fff;
		border-radius: 0.375rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: bold;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.button:hover {
		background-color: var(--primary-color-dark);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
